# Analysis Process Requirements
rule: Describir objective description primero sin hacer assumptions
rule: Comparar cada visual element contra stated modification goals sistemáticamente
rule: Validar through visual measurement para changes involving rotation, position, size, alignment
rule: Buscar activamente evidence que la modificación falló en lugar de succeeded
rule: Challenge whether apparent differences son actually intended differences
rule: Evaluar accessibility compliance y inclusive design implementation
rule: Verificar visual consistency across different platforms y devices
rule: Examinar edge cases, error states, y boundary conditions

# Mandatory Verification Checklist
rule: Describir actual visual content objetivamente
rule: Evitar inferir effects desde code changes
rule: Para rotaciones: confirmar aspect ratio changes
rule: Para positioning: verificar coordinate differences
rule: Para sizing: confirmar dimensional changes
rule: Validar color contrast ratios meet WCAG standards
rule: Verificar focus indicators y keyboard navigation visuals
rule: Verificar responsive breakpoint behavior
rule: Evaluar loading states y transitions
rule: Validar error handling y edge cases
rule: Confirmar design system token compliance
rule: Buscar activamente failure evidence
rule: Questionar whether 'different' equals 'correct'

